Query Strings

  Search Engines dont like this:
    facebook.com?userName=fredrikbjorklund
  They like this:
    facebook.com/user/fredrikbjorklund

    Example2:
      shop.com?products=all <- DONT

      shop.com/products
      shop.com/products/female/shoes/10
      shop.com/products/male/shoes/12


Arrays: Includes, indexOf
